'''The Emperor's Sword''' was a [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]] in the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial Military]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].<ref name="Draw Their Fire" /> Made up of elite [[TIE pilot|pilots]] sworn to defend [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]], the Emperor's Sword was stationed at [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] but always traveled with the Emperor and were therefore present at the [[Death Star II/Legends|Death Star II]] shortly before the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]. As such, they also participated in the squadron parade signifying the Emperor's arrival, alongside its sister squadron [[Emperor's Shield]] and [[Scythe Squadron/Legends|Scythe Squadron]]. Due to the pilots' years of experience, they tended to fly older [[TIE series/Legends|TIE Series]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] such as the [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighter]]. [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]] was put in command of the Emperor's Sword after his role in saving Palpatine from a coup by rogue [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Demetrius Zaarin]].

